skdetail:

Invocation Name: my alzheimers facts
des:
Ask Alexa for facts about Alzheimer’s Disease. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next fact. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
